Jim Meskimen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jim_Meskimen 0 James Ross Meskimen (born September 10, 1959) is an American stand-up comedian, actor, voice actor and impressionist. He is also known for his voice-over work in video games. James_Ross_Meskimen ( born September_10_,_1959 ) is an_American_stand-up_comedian , actor , voice_actor and impressionist .
